					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">The main reason there are so many mappers is that, in Japan, all of the various game companies manufactured their own cartridges and used their own bank switching hardware - in the USA, all boards were made by Nintendo using a strict set of mappers (with some exceptions).</div>

					
						<div class="postbody"><br />_________________<br />Quietust, QMT Productions
<br />P.S. If you don't get this note, let me know and I'll write you another.</div>
