					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle">WedNESday wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">I meant Mhz clock speed for the CPU and PPU.</div>
<br />
<br />NTSC CPU speed is 1.78977272727MHz.
<br />PAL CPU speed is 1.662607MHz.
<br />
<br />PPU speeds can be determined by multiplying by 3 for NTSC or 3.2 for PAL.</div>

					
