<br />
<br /><div class="quotetitle"><b>Quote:</b></div><div class="quotecontent">Talking about the VBlank flag, is it set on the first cycle of the first VBlank scanline? The reason why I ask is Ms. Pacman can apparently experience problems with the VBlank flag being set.</div>Yes. The problem you're speaking of only happens if you let NMI occur always at the same time you set the flag instead of after the current CPU instruction.</div>

